com.function

Class Function

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.function.Storable
      • com.function.Function

  • public class Function
extends Storable
    This class presented function that can have different set of Variable and Param Function e = new Function(new Variable("a", 2.0), new Param("X2")) e.function((a)->{ return a.get("a").value() * a.get("X2").value(); } e.evaluate(new Argument("X2", 2.0));
